  | designation3_number = CN555
  }}
}}
</syntaxhighlight>

{{clear}}
Please note that parameters and other data which appear in both templates should usually be eliminated from one or the other to avoid repeating information. For example, {{tl|Infobox protected area}} already has parameters to display IUCN designations.

